            "title": "盤中速報 - 思佳訊半導體(SWKS-US)大跌5%，報60美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>思佳訊半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SWKS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SWKS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SWKS-US</a>)截至台北時間24日01:18股價下跌3.16美元，報60.00美元，跌幅5%，成交量1,785,285（股），盤中最高價62.90美元、最低價59.97美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.91%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.16%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-2.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.59%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>思佳訊半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SWKS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SWKS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SWKS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+9.82%</li> <li>近 1 月：-17.09%</li> <li>近 3 月：+2.25%</li> <li>近 6 月：+5.85%</li> <li>今年以來：-0.39%</li></ul></section></main>",
